E-commerce and Employee Performance SQL Analysis
Project Overview

This project demonstrates SQL queries to analyze e-commerce orders, payments, and employee performance.
It covers data aggregation, ranking, filtering, window functions, and advanced analytics.

The database contains three main tables:

ecommerce_orders – Stores order details for customers.
ecommerce_payments – Stores payment information for orders.
employee_performance – Contains employee salary and performance data.

The queries include metrics like top performers, revenue trends, discounts, and region-wise analysis.
